{
  "texts": [
    "The present study employs the scientometric database Scopus to examine the adaptation of generative artificial intelligence to the processes of digital transformation in business.",
    "The selection of relevant publications was based on the combination of the keywords \"generative artificial intelligence\" and \"digital transformation\".",
    "A cluster analysis of 42 scientific publications indexed by the Scopus scientometric database during the period 2004-2024 was conducted using the VOSviewer analytical platform.",
    "The software employed the method of relationship density to group 35 keywords into four clusters, which are indicated in Figure 1 by the colours red, blue, green and yellow.",
    "The size of the circle is indicative of the frequency of use of the respective term, with a larger diameter denoting a higher frequency of mention."
  ]
}